                            <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: bold;">4. HTML autocomplete attribute</h3><br>
                            <p>The HTML autocomplete attribute is a newly added attribute of HTML5 which enables an input field to complete aoutomatically. It can have two values "on" and "off" which enables autocomplete either ON or OFF. The default value autocomplete attribute is "on".</p><br>
