                                                                                                                <h3 style="font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; margin: 0.5em0">Pure-CSS lightbox</h3><br>
                                                                                                                <p>The :target pseudo-class is used to create a lightbox without any JavaScript part. This method uses the ability of anchor links to point to those elements that are hidden on the page, by default. When they are targeted, CSS changes their display so as to be shown.</p><br>
                                                                                                                <h3 style="font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: bold; margin: 0.5em 0">Version</h3>
